## 💻 How to Run This Project
To test the implementations on a Linux/WSL environment with QEMU and the RISC-V toolchain installed:

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone [https://github.com/Shihab-cloud/xv6-lottery-scheduler-ticket-lock.git](https://github.com/Shihab-cloud/xv6-lottery-scheduler-ticket-lock.git)
   cd xv6-lottery-scheduler-ticket-lock